<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现存的绝大多数生物，<delay20 />
都是从这间屋子展示的化石所生存的时代开始<delay8 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大量繁衍生息的。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能亲眼见到并感受到<delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这些生活在几亿年前的生物，<delay20 />
也是一种浪漫呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这些家伙<delay8 />到底是怎么
被土壤层层掩埋的？<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直很好奇这个问题<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想，<delay8 />那一定是无论有多强大的意志力<delay8 />
都无法逃过的一场浩劫所导致的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />忽然感觉<delay8 />它们很可怜啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这间屋子里展示的化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它们呈现的生物生活在远古时代，
那时地球表面还几乎被海洋覆盖。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然很难想象，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过……说不定<delay8 />我们祖先的化石，<delay8 />
也放在这间屋子里呢？</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />恐龙就算已经成为化石了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还是很有气势，<delay8 />好帅啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />能看到活着的恐龙，<delay20 />
到底会是一种什么感觉呢？<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是想想<delay8 />都觉得兴奋！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />据说，<delay8 />这里展示的恐龙化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到了晚上<delay8 />就会悄悄地活过来？！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说不定<delay8 />会跑去你家呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈！开玩笑的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可别当真了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />能有机会遇到活的恐龙，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一定要拜托它<delay8 />
收我为徒！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我小时候<delay20 />在图鉴上看到的恐龙，<delay8 />
那可真是太帅了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />长久以来，<delay8 />我一直都很向往那种感觉！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />虽然<delay8 />体型大致能够想象，<delay20 />
但图鉴上画的皮肤颜色<delay8 />不能保证是对的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万一人家是有花纹的，<delay8 />该怎么办？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到在这里展示的这些化石<delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前都是生活在地球上的普通生物，<delay20 />
就感觉感慨万千啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看着<delay8 />这些化石，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也更加觉得<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />应该要珍惜当下的生活。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然说，这件房间里展示的<delay8 />
都是几千万年前的生物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但作为化石它们还算是很年轻的吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是<delay20 />我们这个时代的生物，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一天也会变成化石呢？<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />这都是遥远未来的事了吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然说<delay8 />化石有一种独特的浪漫情怀，<delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是对于<delay8 />变成化石的那个家伙来说，<delay20 />
这绝对是一件<delay8 />很毛骨悚然的事吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过话说回来，<delay8 />就算变成了化石，
也依旧活跃在<delay8 />“展品”的岗位上，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以说是名副其实的有“骨”气了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />化石真的是<delay8 />不管怎么看都不会腻啊！<delay40 />
看着化石想象一下，
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那个时代发生了什么，<delay8 />听起来就很有意思！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的梦想就是，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一天要逛遍<delay8 />
各个岛上的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />站在喜欢的化石面前，<delay20 />
我可以<delay8 />看上几个小时！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好吧，<delay20 />总是盯着人家看，<delay8 />
化石也会不好意思吧。<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />平时<delay8 />我都会掌握好时间的！</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在做鉴定之前，<delay8 />看上去就是块普通的石头。<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但像这样<delay8 />正式成为展品以后，<delay8 />
作为化石还是很有看头的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有了一座这么气派的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
那些被掩埋的化石之谜，
或许就快要等来<delay8 />被破解的一天了！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后，<delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座岛的谜团<delay8 />
也会渐渐解明<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想想就觉得很浪漫呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这间展览室<delay8 />看上去耗费了不少工夫啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能够感受到<colour id="3" />傅达<colour id="65535" />的热忱。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道什么时候，<delay20 />这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上挖掘出来的化石<delay20 />
能够整整齐齐地摆满这间展览室？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />真令人期待！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要来到这里，<delay8 />就能仔仔细细地
观察到各种化石，<delay8 />真是太棒了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要经常过来确认一下，<delay20 />
看看有没有<delay8 />新收集的化石。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好期待<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />今后的发展啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>